name: GO GREEN SEAN DON & DUDE SKYWALKER
description: Black Op Jedi , Dude Skywalker and Money Mind Boss Sean Don have teamed up to bring you the "Go Green" Mixtape. This Mixtape is GUARANTEED to have something for you whether you want conscious Hip-Hop, something to smoke to, or a club jam.

name: BLACK OP SMOKE SESSIONS
description: Belico, Sean Don and Dude Skywalker assembled all of their smoke songs onto one soundtrack to get lit too.

name: DUDE SKYWALKER " SABRES & NEIGHBORS" MIXTAPE
description: Having only been on the mic for a year, Dude has shown mass growth in a short time. With 30 shows under his belt ,the Southern Oregon conscious emcee brings you "Sabres & Neighbors ". "The Dude" compiled a veteran list of guest appearances including Belico, Eddie P, Sean Don and more.

name: HALO DARK "WORTHY" ALBUM
description: Newest Black Op member Halo Dark brings you his first album "Worthy". The Kansas City emcee joined forces with Black Op earlier in 2012 and has been making constant progress since. Teaming with emcees from Oregon, K.C and New Jersey, Halo sets himself apart with his unforgettable voice and one of a kind delivery

name: BELICO "REFINED AUDIO MISCHIEF"ALBUM
description:
HYBRID FUZION DIGITAL/ BLACK OP Proudly present Belico's Refined: Audio Mischief. Produced entirely by Tha Phantoms and Araabmuzik, R.A.M is a delicate blend of Hard edge Hip-Hop and Melodic Bass/Dub. SLated release is scheduled for May 16, 2012. For hard copies and merchandise please visit the Hybrid Fuzion Digital / Black Op facebook page link that is located below. Thank you for you're constant support of Belico Black Op

Recorded by Sean Don for MoneyMind Ent. and Tha Villain for Tha Phantoms.Mastered by Dj OneMic
